0011 digroot: Procedure
0012 /**********************************************************************
0013 * Compute the digital root and persistence of the given decimal number
0014 * 25.07.2012 Walter Pachl
0015 **************************** Bottom of Data **************************/
0016 Parse Arg n                         /* the number                    */
0017 p=0                                 /* persistence                   */
0018 Do While length(n)>1                /* more than one digit in n      */
0019 s=0                               /* initialize sum                */
0020 p=p+1                             /* increment persistence         */
0021 Do while n<>''                    /* as long as there are digits   */
0022 Parse Var n c +1 n              /* pick the first one            */
0023 s=s+c                           /* add to the new sum            */
0024 End
0025 n=s                               /* the 'new' number              */
0026 End
0027 return n p                          /* return root and persistence   */
